Automated tests for rrplayer-fc

Tests are currently in cxxtest[1] format.

To build and run the tests, run 'make'

The Makefile automatically detects and includes any new .h (test suite) files
(test suites) in the built test runner.

How to install cxxtest on Debian:

 cd /tmp/
 wget http://downloads.sourceforge.net/cxxtest/cxxtest-3.10.1-1.noarch.rpm
 fakeroot alien cxxtest-3.10.1-1.noarch.rpm
 sudo dpkg -i cxxtest_3.10.1-2_all.deb

